'''Baga''' was a young [[Bordok/Legends|bordok]] who lived on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. He was the pet of [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]].

==Biography==
Kneesaa received him as a [[Birthday/Legends|birthday]] present from [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket]] and [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]]; the two had spent weeks training him. Kneesaa named him "Baga" because of the sound he made.

